### RemoteGPU API 测试 - 设备管理
### 环境变量配置
@host = http://localhost:8080
@token = {{login.response.body.data.token}}

### 1. 管理员登录获取 Token
# @name login
POST {{host}}/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "admin123"
}

### 2. 获取机器列表
GET {{host}}/api/v1/admin/machines?page=1&page_size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. 创建单台机器
POST {{host}}/api/v1/admin/machines
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "test-gpu-01",
  "hostname": "gpu-server-01",
  "region": "default",
  "ip_address": "192.168.1.100",
  "ssh_port": 22,
  "ssh_username": "root",
  "ssh_password": "your_password"
}

### 4. 检查 Agent 健康状态 (需要设备已添加)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/admin/machines/gpu-server-01/health
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
